<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.2.6">
<l>koṉṟuyi ruṇṇum vicāti pakaipaci tīyaṉa vellām</l>
<l>niṉṟiv vulakil kaṭivāṉ nēmippi rāṉṟamar pōntār</l>
<l>naṉṟicai pāṭiyun tuḷḷi yāṭiyu ñālam parantār</l>
<l>ceṉṟu toḻutuymmiṉ ṟoṇṭīr cintaiyaic cenni ṟuttiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The people of the lord with the discus have come to constantly chase away in this world</l>
<l>all evils [such] as hunger, enmity [and] disease, which kill [and] consume the creatures,</l>
<l>Them who are spread on earth, well singing music and dancing in bounds</l>
<l>go [and] worship [and]	be saved, slaves, having set [your] minds straight [on that].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
